Add GitHub Actions automation system - replaces Vercel Cron

- 6 individual meal time workflows (7AM, 12PM, 3PM, 6PM, 8PM, 10:30PM UTC)
- 8 platform-specific scanning workflows (Reddit, YouTube, Giphy, Pixabay, Bluesky, Imgur, Lemmy, Tumblr)

- Daily automated reporting with health metrics
- Individual workflow isolation prevents cascade failures
- Real-time visibility and manual override capabilities

- Removed Vercel cron job from vercel.json
- Meal posting now distributed across 6 independent workflows
- Platform scanning optimized with staggered timing to avoid rate limits
- Schedule display now shows actual posting status vs time-based estimates
